data.description:
This modern-style home boasts a small town atmosphere just minutes away from Altus. With three bedrooms, two bathrooms, and two living areas, this property offers ample space for comfortable living. Additionally, a bonus room with an exterior entrance from the patio and a full bath provides versatility for storage, an office, or even a fourth bedroom.

The kitchen features updated concrete countertops, a pantry with pull-out drawers,m, a black granite sink, and built-in black/stainless appliances including a refrigerator, stove top, oven, and microwave. The large entry leads to the first living area with a gas log fireplace, nice built-in shelving, and a reading nook. The dining area boasts a stained concrete floor, while the second living area features windows all around looking out to a large fenced backyard.

This property also includes two backyard patios, one of which is partially covered, making it ideal for entertaining. The main ensuite offers a large shower, a good-sized bedroom, and a huge closet with built-ins. Other features of this home include white woodwork, ceiling fans, and window blinds. The oversized two-car garage includes a storage closet, insulated garage door and electric car charging station. The exterior of the home is vinyl siding with gutters, and the roof was replaced in 2019 while the AC was replaced in 2020.

To schedule a viewing of this exceptional property, please call listing agent today!
